'''動視暴雪'''（{{Lang-en|Activision Blizzard, Inc.}}，{{Nasdaq|ATVI}}）是一家位於[[美國|美國]][[加利福尼亞州|加利福尼亞州]][[圣莫尼卡|-{zh-hans:圣莫尼卡;zh-hk:聖莫尼卡;zh-tw:聖塔莫尼卡;}-市]]的電子遊戲[[控股公司|控股公司]]。<ref>{{cite news|title=Top 5 Mutual Fund Holders of Activision Blizzard (ATVI, FOCPX)|first=Evan|last=Tarver|url=http://www.investopedia.com/articles/investing/031516/top-5-mutual-fund-holders-activision-blizzard-atvi-focpx.asp|publisher=[[Investopedia|Investopedia]]|date=2016-03-15|access-date=2016-03-29|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160320051714/http://www.investopedia.com/articles/investing/031516/top-5-mutual-fund-holders-activision-blizzard-atvi-focpx.asp|archive-date=2016-03-20}}</ref>此公司於2008年7月經由動視（[[动视发行|动视发行]]的上市母公司）與[[威望迪遊戲|威望迪遊戲]]兩間公司合併所創立。動視暴雪在[[纳斯达克|纳斯达克]]交易所底下以ATVI的代號交易，<ref name="ukgamespotabrendan">{{Cite web|title=Vivendi CEO Activision Blizzard's new chairman|url=http://uk.gamespot.com/pc/action/callofduty5/news.html?sid=6209171&mode=news|access-date=2009-08-27|author=Thorsen|date=2009-05-05|first=Tor|publisher=GameSpot|archive-url=https://archive.today/20120717071345/http://uk.gamespot.com/pc/action/callofduty5/news.html?sid=6209171&mode=news|archive-date=2012-07-17}}</ref>且從2005年起為[[標準普爾500指數|標準普爾500指數]]的組成股票之一。<ref name="actsp500">{{Cite news|title=Call of Duty publisher Activision Blizzard joins the S&P 500|first=Dean|author=Takahashi|url=https://venturebeat.com/2015/08/27/call-of-duty-publisher-activision-blizzard-joins-the-sp-500/|work=[[VentureBeat|VentureBeat]]|date=2015-08-27|accessdate=2015-10-23|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150905054750/http://venturebeat.com/2015/08/27/call-of-duty-publisher-activision-blizzard-joins-the-sp-500/|archivedate=2015-09-05}}</ref>動視暴雪目前由五個單位組成：<ref name="ourcompany">{{Cite web|title=Activision - Blizzard: Our Company|url=http://www.activisionblizzard.com/about-us|access-date=2016-01-11|work=activisionblizzard.com|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160118022108/http://activisionblizzard.com/about-us|archive-date=2016-01-18}}</ref>[[动视|動視發行]]、[[暴雪娛樂|暴雪娛樂]]、[[King_(遊戲公司)|King]]、<ref name="nyt-activisionking">{{Cite news|title=Activision Blizzard to Buy King Digital, Maker of Candy Crush|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2015/11/03/business/dealbook/activision-blizzardto-buy-king-digital-maker-of-candy-crush.html|accessdate=2015-11-03|work=The New York Times|date=2015-11-02|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151106210442/http://www.nytimes.com/2015/11/03/business/dealbook/activision-blizzardto-buy-king-digital-maker-of-candy-crush.html|archivedate=2015-11-06}}</ref>[[MLG|MLG]]（大聯盟遊戲）<ref name="advistionbeefsup">{{Cite web|title=Activision Blizzard beefs up e-sports muscle|url=http://www.cnet.com/news/activision-blizzard-beefs-up-e-sports-muscle/|access-date=2016-01-04|work=CNET|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160103201140/http://www.cnet.com/news/activision-blizzard-beefs-up-e-sports-muscle/|archive-date=2016-01-03}}</ref>以及[[動視暴雪影業|動視暴雪影業]]。<ref name="fortuneesportsa">{{Cite web|title=Why Activision-Blizzard just launched a new eSports division|url=http://fortune.com/2015/10/22/activision-blizzard-new-esports-division/|access-date=2015-11-13|author=Morris|date=2015-10-22|first=Chris|work=[[Fortune_(magazine)|Fortune]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151110225337/http://fortune.com/2015/10/22/activision-blizzard-new-esports-division/|archive-date=2015-11-10}}</ref><ref name="goldfrbskylander">{{Cite news|author=Goldfarb|first=Andrew|title=Call of Duty Movie, Skylander TV Show Headline New Activision Blizzard Film Studio|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2015/11/06/call-of-duty-movie-skylanders-tv-show-headline-new-activision-film-studio|accessdate=2015-11-06|work=[[IGN|IGN]]|date=2015-11-06|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151106193815/http://www.ign.com/articles/2015/11/06/call-of-duty-movie-skylanders-tv-show-headline-new-activision-film-studio|archivedate=2015-11-06}}</ref>

