y: Modern Warfare 3 Shatters All Sales Records|url=http://kotaku.com/5857400/call-of-duty-modern-warfare-3-shatters-all-sales-records-surprises-no-one|access-date=2011-11-11|author=Crecente|date=2011-11-11|first=Brian|publisher=Kotaku|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111113070522/http://kotaku.com/5857400/call-of-duty-modern-warfare-3-shatters-all-sales-records-surprises-no-one|archive-date=2011-11-13}}</ref>也是《[[決勝時刻系列|決勝時刻]]》系列連續第三年打破紀錄；2010年的《[[決勝時刻：黑色行動|決勝時刻：黑色行動]]》於第一天收入3.6億美元；2009年的《[[決勝時刻：現代戰爭2|決勝時刻：現代戰爭2]]》則收入3.1億美元。<ref name="next-genbiz">{{Cite web|title=MW3 Breaks Black Ops Launch Record|url=http://www.next-gen.biz/news/modern-warfare-3-breaks-black-ops-launch-record|access-date=2011-11-11|date=2011-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111112094950/http://www.next-gen.biz/news/modern-warfare-3-breaks-black-ops-launch-record|archive-date=2011-11-12}}</ref>《[[決勝時刻：黑色行動3|決勝時刻：黑色行動3]]》也於2015年銷售周末期間收入5.5億美元，創下當年最高的娛樂銷售紀錄。<ref name="polygonselling">[http://www.polygon.com/2015/11/11/9715060/call-of-duty-black-ops-3-sales-advanced-warfare-ghosts Call of Duty: Black Ops 3 selling 'significantly' better than Advanced Warfare and Ghosts] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160408060504/http://www.polygon.com/2015/11/11/9715060/call-of-duty-black-ops-3-sales-advanced-warfare-ghosts|date=2016-04-08}} By Samit Sarkar on November 11, 2015 at 5:30p @SamitSarkar</ref><ref name="techspotbest">{{Cite web|title='Call of Duty: Black Ops III' was the best-selling game of 2015|url=http://www.techspot.com/news/63496-call-duty-black-ops-iii-best-selling-game.html|access-date=2016-01-28|author=Knight|date=2016-01-15|first=Shawn|publisher=[[TechSpot|TechSpot]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160118054124/http://www.techspot.com/news/63496-call-duty-black-ops-iii-best-selling-game.html|archive-date=2016-01-18}}</ref>

2011年，動視暴雪推出了《[[寶貝龍世界系列|寶貝龍世界]]》系列，<ref name="BKiSpyro">{{Cite web|title=Bobby Kotick On Hatching Skylanders: Spyro's Adventure|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/davidewalt/2011/07/29/bobby-kotick-skylanders-spiros-adventure/|access-date=2015-08-29|author=Ewalt|date=2011-07-29|first=David|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150527040751/http://www.forbes.com/sites/davidewalt/2011/07/29/bobby-kotick-skylanders-spiros-adventure/|archive-date=2015-05-27}}</ref>當時的新聞媒體認可動視暴雪發明並推展{{Translink|en|Toys-to-life|玩具連動類遊戲}}的創新之舉。<ref name="BKiSpyro" /><ref>{{Cite web|title=Skylanders story|url=http://www.polygon.com/2014/4/16/5614716/skylanders-story-toys-for-bob-skylanders-swap-force|access-date=2015-08-29|date=2014-04-16|publisher=polygon.com|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150901050142/http://www.polygon.com/2014/4/16/5614716/skylanders-story-toys-for-bob-skylanders-swap-force|archive-date=2015-09-01}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|title=With Skylanders Giants, Activision could dominate toys and video games (video and gallery)|first=Dean|author=Takahashi|url=https://venturebeat.com/2012/06/05/with-skylanders-giants-will-activision-rule-dominate-toys-and-video-games-video-interview-and-gallery/|work=[[VentureBeat|VentureBeat]]|date=2012-06-05|accessdate=2015-08-29|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160122115421/http://venturebeat.com/2012/06/05/with-skylanders-giants-will-activision-rule-dominate-toys-and-video-games-video-interview-and-gallery/|archivedate=2016-01-22}}</ref>系列第一作《{{Translink|en|Skylanders: Spyro's Adventure}}》於2011年國際玩具業協會（{{lang|en|Toy Industry Association}}）獲提名兩樣獎項：「年度遊戲獎」與「年度創新玩具獎」。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Toy Industry Unveils Nominees for 2012 Toy of the Year (TOTY) Awards; Announces Inductees into Toy Industry Hall of Fame|url=http://www.toyassociation.org/AM/Template.cfm?Section=Home&TEMPLATE=/CM/ContentDisplay.cfm&CONTENTID=16688|access-date=2017-07-08|author=Appell|first=Adrienne|publisher=[[Toy_Industry_Association|Toy Industry Association]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120607160341/http://www.toyassociation.org/AM/Template.cfm?Section=Home&TEMPLATE=%2FCM%2FContentDisplay.cfm&CONTENTID=16688|archive-date=2012-06-07}}</ref>《Skylanders: Spyro's Adventure》與其續作接著在各大主機平台與PC平台上推出，其中也有許多在手機平台上推出。<ref name="BKiSpyro" />

=== 2013年－2014年：與威望迪分離與成長 ===
[[File:Activision-Gamescom_2013.JPG|右]]展示2013年的遊戲作品，像是[[決勝時刻：魅影|決勝時刻：魅影]]與''Skylanders: Swap Force''。]]
2013年7月25日，動視暴雪宣布以58.3億美元向其擁有者威望迪購買4.29億股，使威望迪的持有股份百分比於9月成交後，從原本的63%掉到11.8%。<ref name="transofmrativepurchase">{{Cite web|title=Activision Blizzard Announces Transformative Purchase of Shares from Vivendi and New Capital Structure|url=http://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20130725006767/en/Activision-Blizzard-Announces-Transformative-Purchase-Shares-Vivendi|access-date=2013-07-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130728104839/http://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20130725006767/en/Activision-Blizzard-Announces-Transformative-Purchase-Shares-Vivendi|archive-date=2013-07-28}}</ref>交易完成後，威望迪不再是動視暴雪的母公司，<ref>{{Cite news|title=Activision Blizzard completes buyback from Vivendi Universal in multi-billion dollar deal|first=Timothy|author=Seppala|url=https://www.engadget.com/2013/10/13/activision-blizzard-vivendi-buyout/|publisher=[[Engadget|Engadget]]|date=2013-10-13|accessdate=2015-08-29|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160103075959/http://www.engadget.com/2013/10/13/activision-blizzard-vivendi-buyout/|archivedate=2016-01-03}}</ref>而動視暴雪則因其大多股份被公開持有，而成為一間獨立的公司。波比·科蒂克與白賴仁·凱利保有共24.4%的公司股份。並且，科蒂克保留其總裁與執行長的職位，而白賴仁·凱利則為新董事長。<ref name="transofmrativepurchase" />2013年10月12日，在{{Translink|en|Delaware Supreme Court|德拉瓦州最高法院}}同意不久後，動視暴雪照著計劃完成了買回。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Activision Blizzard completes buyback from Vivendi|url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/activision-blizzard-completes-buyback-from-vivendi/1100-6415550/|access-date=2013-10-15|author=Makuch|date=2013-10-12|first=Eddie|publisher=GameSpot|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131015054126/http://www.gamespot.com/articles/activision-blizzard-completes-buyback-from-vivendi/1100-6415550/|archive-date=2013-10-15}}</ref>威望迪隨後於2014年5月22日賣出其剩餘股份的一半，使擁有權降低至5.8%。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Vivendi to sell 41.5 million Activision Blizzard shares|url=http://www.vivendi.com/press/press-releases/vivendi-to-sell-41-5-million-activision-blizzard-shares-22-may-2014/|access-date=2014-07-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714232325/http://www.vivendi.com/press/press-releases/vivendi-to-sell-41-5-million-activision-blizzard-shares-22-may-2014/|archive-date=2014-07-14}}</ref>並在兩年後完全脫離動視暴雪。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Vivendi Sells Remaining Activision Blizzard Stake to Unknown Buyer|url=https://www.gamespot.com/articles/vivendi-sells-remaining-activision-blizzard-stake-/1100-6433856/|access-date=2018-01-23|author=Hussain|date=2016-01-15|first=Tamoor|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171002070555/https://www.gamespot.com/articles/vivendi-sells-remaining-activision-blizzard-stake-/1100-6433856/|archive-date=2017-10-02}}</ref>

2014年9月9日，動視暴雪釋出全新遊戲《[[天命_(遊戲)|天命]]》。該作在銷售當日銷售額超過5億美元，打破全新遊戲系列作首日銷售紀錄。<ref name="BKaforbesonff">{{Cite news|title='Destiny' Crosses $500 Million On Day One, Biggest New Video Game Launch Ever|first=Erik|author=Kain|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/erikkain/2014/09/10/destiny-crosses-500-million-on-day-one-biggest-new-video-game-launch-ever/|work=[[Forbes|Forbes]]|date=2014-09-10|accessdate=2015-08-29|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140910192609/http://www.forbes.com/sites/erikkain/2014/09/10/destiny-crosses-500-million-on-day-one-biggest-new-video-game-launch-ever/|archivedate=2014-09-10}}</ref>動視暴雪推出《[[決勝時刻：魅影|決勝時刻：魅影]]》，其編劇為影視編劇[[史蒂芬·加漢|史蒂芬·加漢]]，<ref>{{Cite news|title=Challenge for Activision CEO: capitalizing on next-gen game consoles|first=Dawn|author=Chmielewski|url=http://articles.latimes.com/2013/dec/10/entertainment/la-et-ct-bobby-kotick-activision-ceo-20131210|work=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]]|date=2013-12-10|accessdate=2015-08-29|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151024182236/http://articles.latimes.com/2013/dec/10/entertainment/la-et-ct-bobby-kotick-activision-ceo-20131210|archivedate=2015-10-24}}</ref>他曾為《[[諜對諜|-{zh-hans:辛瑞那;zh-hk:油激暗戰;zh-tw:諜對諜;}-]]》（兼任導演）、《[[圍城13天：阿拉莫戰役|圍城13天：阿拉莫戰役]]》、《[[毒品网络|-{zh-hans:毒品网络;zh-hk:毒網;zh-tw:天人交戰;}-]]》等電影編寫劇本。發售當日，該遊戲在零售商店賣出10億美元的驚人銷售額。<ref name="BKaforbesonff" />2014年，動視暴雪成為全球收入第五高的[[电子游戏公司列表|遊戲公司]]，<ref>{{Cite web|title=The Top 25 Public Companies Generated $54.1Bn Game Revenues in 2014, Up 10.4% Year-on-Year|url=http://www.newzoo.com/insights/the-top-25-public-companies-generated-54-1bn-game-revenues-in-2014-up-10-4-year-on-year/|access-date=2015-05-22|date=2015-04-20|publisher=NewZoo|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150522133829/http://www.newzoo.com/insights/the-top-25-public-companies-generated-54-1bn-game-revenues-in-2014-up-10-4-year-on-year/|archive-date=2015-05-22}}</ref>總資產共147.46億美元，並擁有共75.13億美元的[[股東權益|資產淨值]]。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Activision Blizzard - Annual Report 2013|url=http://files.shareholder.com/downloads/ACTI/3305760073x0x746096/2205B72D-1007-4DCB-A5F1-2D121D8EC95C/Activision_Blizzard_2013_AR.1.pdf|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714174237/http://files.shareholder.com/downloads/ACTI/3305760073x0x746096/2205B72D-1007-4DCB-A5F1-2D121D8EC95C/Activision_Blizzard_2013_AR.1.pdf|archive-date=2014-07-14}}</ref>

=== 2015年至2021年：標普500與新部門 ===
動視暴雪於2015年8月28日獲納入[[标准普尔500指数|标准普尔500指数]]成份股，成為其中與電子遊戲有關的兩間公司之一，另一間則是其競爭對手[[艺电|EA]]。<ref name="actsp500">{{Cite news|title=Call of Duty publisher Activision Blizzard joins the S&P 500|first=Dean|author=Takahashi|url=https://venturebeat.com/2015/08/27/call-of-duty-publisher-activision-blizzard-joins-the-sp-500/|work=[[VentureBeat|VentureBeat]]|date=2015-08-27|accessdate=2015-10-23|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150905054750/http://venturebeat.com/2015/08/27/call-of-duty-publisher-activision-blizzard-joins-the-sp-500/|archivedate=2015-09-05}}</ref>9月推出《寶貝龍》系列續作，為玩具連動類遊戲領域加入了載具要素。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Skylanders SuperChargers adds vehicles to the list|url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2015-06-03-skylanders-superchargers-adds-vehicles-to-the-mix|access-date=2015-06-03|author=Yin-Poole|date=2015-06-03|first=Wesley|work=[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150706115106/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2015-06-03-skylanders-superchargers-adds-vehicles-to-the-mix|archive-date=2015-07-06}}</ref>9月15日，動視與Bungie推出《天命》的全新章節—《{{Translink|en|Destiny: The Taken King|天命：復仇之王}}》。兩天後，[[索尼|索尼]]宣布該作打破[[PlayStation|PlayStation]]平台銷售當日下載量紀錄，包含總玩家數和同時上線人數。<ref>{{Cite news|title=Destiny: The Taken King claims PSN's records|first=Ben|author=Parfitt|url=http://www.mcvuk.com/news/read/destiny-the-taken-king-claims-psn-s-records/0156101|publisher=MCV - UK|date=2015-09-18|accessdate=2015-10-23|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151022112952/http://www.mcvuk.com/news/read/destiny-the-taken-king-claims-psn-s-records/0156101|archivedate=2015-10-22}}</ref>

動視暴雪在11月以59億美元收購遊戲公司[[King_(遊戲公司)|King]]，也就是休閒遊戲《[[Candy_Crush_Saga|Candy Crush Saga]]》的製作者。<ref name="nyt-activisionking">{{Cite news|title=Activision Blizzard to Buy King Digital, Maker of Candy Crush|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2015/11/03/business/dealbook/activision-blizzardto-buy-king-digital-maker-of-candy-crush.html|accessdate=2015-11-03|work=The New York Times|date=2015-11-02|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151106210442/http://www.nytimes.com/2015/11/03/business/dealbook/activision-blizzardto-buy-king-digital-maker-of-candy-crush.html|archivedate=2015-11-06}}</ref>

同月，動視暴雪宣布組成[[動視暴雪影業|動視暴雪影業]]，一間專門生產動視暴雪旗下遊戲相關影視作品的[[製片公司|製片公司]]，<ref name="goldfrbskylander">{{Cite news|author=Goldfarb|first=Andrew|title=Call of Duty Movie, Skylander TV Show Headline New Activision Blizzard Film Studio|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2015/11/06/call-of-duty-movie-skylanders-tv-show-headline-new-activision-film-studio|accessdate=2015-11-06|work=[[IGN|IGN]]|date=2015-11-06|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151106193815/http://www.ign.com/articles/2015/11/06/call-of-duty-movie-skylanders-tv-show-headline-new-activision-film-studio|archivedate=2015-11-06}}</ref>並由製作人[[史黛西·舒爾|史黛西·舒爾]]（作品包括[[低俗小说|-{zh-hans:低俗小说;zh-hk:危險人物;zh-tw:黑色追緝令;}-]]、[[永不妥協|-{zh-hans:永不妥协;zh-hk:伊人當自強;zh-tw:永不妥協;}-]]、[[世贸中心_(电影)|世貿中心]]、[[全境擴散|-{zh-hans:传染病;zh-hk:世紀戰疫;zh-tw:全境擴散;}-]]、[[被解救的姜戈|-{zh-hans:被解救的姜戈;zh-hk:黑殺令;zh-tw:決殺令;}-]]等）與前[[华特迪士尼公司|迪士尼]]高層尼克·范戴克（{{lang|en|Nick van Dyk}}）共同領導。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Activision Blizzard recruits ex-Tarantino producer to turn its video games into films|url=https://www.theverge.com/2016/1/13/10759524/activision-blizzard-studios-films-stacey-sher|access-date=2018-12-19|author=Vincent|date=2016-01-13|first=James|work=The Verge|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181209123944/https://www.theverge.com/2016/1/13/10759524/activision-blizzard-studios-films-stacey-sher|archive-date=2018-12-09}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/technology/2017/apr/05/call-of-duty-franchise-activision-blizzard-next-disney-marvel-film-franchise|title=Could the Call of Duty franchise be the next Marvel?|author=Jackson|first=Jasper|date=2017-04-05|work=The Guardian|accessdate=2018-12-19|language=en-GB|issn=0261-3077|archivedate=2018-12-09|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20181209212628/https://www.theguardian.com/technology/2017/apr/05/call-of-duty-franchise-activision-blizzard-next-disney-marvel-film-franchise}}</ref>

2017年6月，動視暴雪打進[[財富美國500強|財富美國500強]]，成為繼[[雅達利|雅達利]]和EA後，第三間被列入該榜的遊戲公司。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Activision Blizzard Aims for the Big Leagues|url=http://fortune.com/2017/06/07/fortune-500-activision-blizzard/|access-date=2018-01-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180125093844/http://fortune.com/2017/06/07/fortune-500-activision-blizzard/|archive-date=2018-01-25}}</ref>

科蒂克在2019年2月時舉行的2018財政年度股東會議中表示，雖然公司的年度營收打破紀錄，他們還是會開除接近755名員工，佔公司非管理階層員工約8%。他指「將不再以沒有達到期望的人員為主要考量，並減少全公司特定幾樣非開發與管理相關的支出」。<ref name="arstech feb2019" />科蒂克聲明他們將把更多資源投入於開發團隊，並專注於發展[[電子競技|電子競技]]、Battle.net服務和《Candy Crush Saga》、《決勝時刻》、《鬥陣特攻》、《魔獸》、《暗黑破壞神》、《爐石戰記》這些主打遊戲。在這之前，動視暴雪與Bungie同意取消《[[命运2|天命2]]》的發行合約，因為該作的收入不如預期，而Bungie則保留對《天命》的掌控權。<ref name="arstech feb2019">{{Cite web|title=Activision-Blizzard lays off 775 people after "record results in 2018"|url=https://arstechnica.com/gaming/2019/02/activision-blizzard-lays-off-775-people-after-record-results-in-2018/|access-date=2019-02-12|author=Axon|date=2019-02-12|first=Samuel|work=[[Ars_Technica|Ars Technica]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190212234817/https://arstechnica.com/gaming/2019/02/activision-blizzard-lays-off-775-people-after-record-results-in-2018/|archive-date=2019-02-12}}</ref>這決定使動視暴雪在其2018年度財務報表中加入1.64億美元的收入。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Activision reports $164 million in revenue from handing Destiny back to Bungie|url=https://www.pcgamesn.com/destiny-2/bungie-activision-contract|access-date=2019-03-02|author=Bailey|date=2019-03-01|first=Dustin|work=[[PCGamesN|PCGamesN]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190302063337/https://www.pcgamesn.com/destiny-2/bungie-activision-contract|archive-date=2019-03-02}}</ref>

丹尼爾·亞雷格里（{{lang|en|Daniel Alegre}}）於2020年4月7日取代柯迪·約翰遜（{{lang|en|Coddy Johnson}}）成為動視暴雪的新任總裁，約翰遜調遷至一個特殊的顧問職位。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Activision Blizzard Has A New President -- Here's How Much Money He Makes|url=https://www.gamespot.com/articles/activision-blizzard-has-a-new-president-heres-how-/1100-6474690/|access-date=2020-03-11|author=Makuch|date=2020-03-11|first=Eddie|work=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]|archive-date=2020-07-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200726142923/https://www.gamespot.com/articles/activision-blizzard-appoints-new-president-heres-h/1100-6474690/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2020年第二季度期間，世界各地因應[[COVID-19|COVID-19]]疫情而推出封鎖措施，帶動線上遊戲需求增長，動視暴雪於數位方面的營利達到14.4億美元。<ref>{{Cite news|date=2020-05-06|title=Lockdown and loaded: virus triggers video game boost|language=en-GB|work=BBC News|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/business-52555277|accessdate=2020-05-06|archivedate=2020-07-09|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200709090259/https://www.bbc.com/news/business-52555277}}</ref>2021年1月時，受惠於上述原因，動視暴雪的預估市值達720億美元。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Activision Blizzard is currently valued at $72 billion|url=https://www.pcgamer.com/activision-blizzard-is-currently-valued-at-dollar72-billion/|access-date=2021-01-21|author=Taylor|date=2021-01-21|first=Mollie|work=[[PC_Gamer|PC Gamer]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210121145151/https://www.pcgamer.com/activision-blizzard-is-currently-valued-at-dollar72-billion/|archive-date=2021-01-21}}</ref>

[[沙烏地阿拉伯公共投資基金|沙烏地阿拉伯公共投資基金]]於2021年2月買入動視暴雪1,490萬股，價值14億美元。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Saudi investment fund acquires shares in Activision Blizzard, Take-Two, and EA|url=https://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/377610/Saudi_investment_fund_acquires_shares_in_Activision_Blizzard_TakeTwo_and_EA_.php|access-date=2021-02-18|author=Kerr|date=2021-02-18|first=Chris|work=[[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]]|archive-date=2021-02-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210218155641/https://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/377610/Saudi_investment_fund_acquires_shares_in_Activision_Blizzard_TakeTwo_and_EA_.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>

動視暴雪於2021年4月宣布科蒂克將繼續保留其執行長職位到2023年4月，並同意減薪50%，即875,000美元。但他還是保留獎金收入的權利，即使他同意將目標獎金降低50%，根據公司的表現，他仍有可能得到高達他薪資兩倍的獎金。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Activision Blizzard CEO Bobby Kotick takes 50% pay cut|url=https://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/2021-04-29-activision-blizzard-ceo-bobby-kotick-takes-50-percent-pay-cut|access-date=2021-04-29|author=Partis|date=2021-04-29|first=Danielle|work=[[GamesIndustry.biz|GamesIndustry.biz]]|archive-date=2022-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220121114015/https://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/2021-04-29-activision-blizzard-ceo-bobby-kotick-takes-50-percent-pay-cut|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 2022年至今：被微软收购 ===
