=== 職場行為案 ===
2021年7月20日，{{Translink|en|California Department of Fair Employment and Housing|加州公平就業與住房部}}（{{Lang-en|California Department of Fair Employment and Housing}}）在經過約兩年的調查後，向法院就該公司內部長年存在的[[性別歧視|性別歧視]]及[[性騷擾|性騷擾]]問題提起訴訟<ref>{{Cite web|title=「動視暴雪」爆長年性騷擾、歧視女員工 兄弟會文化遭加州政府起訴|url=https://dq.yam.com/post.php?id=14110|access-date=2021-08-06|date=2021-07-23|last=阿雀|work=地球圖輯隊|language=zh-TW|archive-date=2021-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210806052739/https://dq.yam.com/post.php?id=14110|dead-url=no}}</ref>。指控相關細節提及公司對女性員工有不當行為，與公司內有「[[兄弟會與姊妹會|兄弟會]]文化」（{{Lang-en|'frat boy' culture}}）。<ref name="bloomberglaw DFEH" />管理階層原先否認相關指控，導致員工批判管理階層對待此事態度隨便。<ref name="bloomberglaw DFEH">{{Cite web|title=Activision Blizzard Sued Over 'Frat Boy' culture, Harassment|url=https://news.bloomberglaw.com/daily-labor-report/activision-blizzard-sued-by-california-over-frat-boy-culture|author=Allsup|date=2021-07-21|first=Maeve|work=Bloomberg Law|access-date=2021-08-27|archive-date=2021-08-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210802155138/https://news.bloomberglaw.com/daily-labor-report/activision-blizzard-sued-by-california-over-frat-boy-culture|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=California sues Activision Blizzard over alleged harassment|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/technology-57929543|date=2021-07-21|work=BBC|access-date=2021-08-27|archive-date=2021-07-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210727133342/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/technology-57929543|dead-url=no}}</ref>即使波比·科蒂克在對員工發表的公開信內表示管理層原先反應不當，並會進一步處理相關事件後，員工們仍針對公司的應對態度與行動開始進行罷工抗議。<ref name="verge walkout">{{Cite web|title=Activision Blizzard employees to walk out following sexual harassment lawsuit|url=https://www.theverge.com/2021/7/27/22595922/activision-blizzard-employees-walk-out-sexual-harassment|access-date=2021-07-27|author=Schiffer|date=2021-07-27|first=Zoe|work=[[The_Verge|The Verge]]|archive-date=2021-07-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210728181733/https://www.theverge.com/2021/7/27/22595922/activision-blizzard-employees-walk-out-sexual-harassment|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://game.nownews.com/news/20210723/3299559/ |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-08-18 |archive-date=2021-08-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210818132632/https://game.nownews.com/news/20210723/3299559/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://game.udn.com/game/story/122089/5633747 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-08-18 |archive-date=2021-10-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211016042557/https://game.udn.com/game/story/122089/5633747 |dead-url=no }}</ref>該案成為遊戲開發產業內的重大爭論議題，涉及[[＃MeToo|＃MeToo]]運動，與缺少[[工會|工會]]保護員工的問題等要點。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2021/07/29/technology/activision-walkout-metoo-call-of-duty.html|title=Activision, Facing Internal Turmoil, Grapples With #MeToo Reckoning|first=Kellen|author=Browning|first2=Mike|author2=Isaac|date=2021-07-29|accessdate=2021-07-30|work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|archive-date=2021-07-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210730002921/https://www.nytimes.com/2021/07/29/technology/activision-walkout-metoo-call-of-duty.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=What Can Activision's Own Investigation of Harassment Actually Accomplish?|url=https://www.vice.com/en/article/akgade/what-can-activisions-own-investigation-of-harassment-actually-accomplish|access-date=2021-08-02|author=Gurley|date=2021-07-29|first=Lauren Kaori|work=Vice Waypoint|archive-date=2021-08-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210801100557/https://www.vice.com/en/article/akgade/what-can-activisions-own-investigation-of-harassment-actually-accomplish|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Activision Blizzard Employees Walk Out, as Company Hires Law Firm Known for Union-Busting|url=https://www.pastemagazine.com/games/activision-blizzard/activision-blizzard-walkout-part-2/|access-date=2021-08-02|author=Long|date=2021-07-30|first=Katherine|work=[[Paste_(magazine)|Paste]]|archive-date=2021-08-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210802203437/https://www.pastemagazine.com/games/activision-blizzard/activision-blizzard-walkout-part-2/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

